{"tid":960141,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"2019年既屯門人有福氣啦，新輕鐵購2019年內投入服務","createTime":"2018-12-29T07:11:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-29T08:41:19.000Z","uid":213877,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6179f950b558f66075c8dee3e369c40fdce4188e","tid":960141,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T07:11:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2262405/org/c962cf14d29b98d079c043e297e208c5.jpg/vztV4qiXEpTJNoy2aqiELLouh4x10GoCQanC2UGpwtk?v=w1120r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2262405%2Forg%2Fc962cf14d29b98d079c043e297e208c5.jpg%2FvztV4qiXEpTJNoy2aqiELLouh4x10GoCQanC2UGpwtk%3Fv%3Dw1120r16_9&h=5dbd44fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n淨望張圖都覺得一陣柒味"},{"pid":"797beceedb3e419ff513b93c583134d68d507072","tid":960141,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T07:11:49.000Z","msg":"港鐵今日（28）表示，兩輛從內地購買的全新輕鐵列車，今日運抵港鐵屯門車廠。港鐵指，車身外觀設計承襲上一代，車廂內則安裝了經改良的LED照明系統，以及改進了扶手分佈，預計於明年內投入服務。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵於2016年向內地的中車南京浦鎮車輛有限公司，採購40輛新輕鐵，其中30輛用以更換現有的輕鐵，其餘10輛則用作擴充車隊，令輕鐵數量於2023年，增至150輛。港鐵指，其餘新車將於明年至2023年間分批運抵香港。<br />\n<br />\n外表方面，港鐵表示，新一代輕鐵的外觀及色調承襲上一代設計，車輛頭尾兩端外型線條鮮明；而駕駛室亦可為車長提供更廣闊的視野。車廂方面，則安裝了經改良的LED照明系統，加強空間感；並改進了扶手和吊環的分佈，期望為乘客帶來更佳乘車經驗。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵：必須通過所有安全測試<br />\n<br />\n港鐵稱，新車抵港前，已在製造商廠房接受連串測試及查驗，之後會再作進一步的測試。港鐵續指，所有新輕鐵必須通過所有安全及服務表現測試，並須獲相關政府部門審批，才可投入服務，預計新車於明年內投入運作。"},{"pid":"e6f629215b58310f3cab0c8cd06256c34a9d6f86","tid":960141,"uid":28831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T07:12:29.000Z","msg":"仆街了<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fff3d36010efae5b831efa3e614feb73d58720b","tid":960141,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e6f629215b58310f3cab0c8cd06256c34a9d6f86","tid":960141,"uid":28831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T07:12:29.000Z","msg":"仆街了<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T07:12:57.000Z","msg":"有新車你坐有幾仆街？<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9b362fdcb0a69723290e1db9645cb4689b192ee","tid":960141,"uid":52595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T07:14:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ae70535bb8a4f85ab25f7b496c2e425768ca14ec","tid":960141,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T07:15:01.000Z","msg":"lm睇出軌/爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6750a8a70246711c0ecca8527cc24e2f0ddd4a6c","tid":960141,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f9b362fdcb0a69723290e1db9645cb4689b192ee","tid":960141,"uid":52595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T07:14:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T07:15:20.000Z","msg":"所以咪有新車坐囉<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n輕鐵又有機會加票價啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c56ee4776a84e30ef779c5909c77b9f5c76cab05","tid":960141,"uid":28831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4fff3d36010efae5b831efa3e614feb73d58720b","tid":960141,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e6f629215b58310f3cab0c8cd06256c34a9d6f86","tid":960141,"uid":28831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T07:12:29.000Z","msg":"仆街了<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T07:12:57.000Z","msg":"有新車你坐有幾仆街？<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T07:15:44.000Z","msg":"屌你老母我住屯門呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"